=== VOID_SINGER ===
# id: 26
# title: The Void Singer
# chinese_title: 虚空歌者
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

A translucent being drifts through the vacuum outside the station's viewport, its body trailing bioluminescent filaments. It presses against the glass and sings — a vibration you feel rather than hear. The melody carries emotions: curiosity, loneliness, wonder.

* [Press your hand against the glass in greeting]
  ~ gain_radical("心")
  "心" (xīn) — heart, emotion
* [Record its song on your equipment]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "歌" (gē) — song, to sing
* [Try to communicate using light patterns]
  ~ gain_radical("月")
  "月" (yuè) — moon, month
* [Close the blast shutters]
  ~ nothing
  "关" (guān) — to close, to shut
